# agent-runtime project work_dir gitignore template.
# Bootstrap renders this into <work_dir>/.gitignore (only if the directory
# is a git repo and no .gitignore exists yet) so feishu image cache and
# other transient runtime state never leak into the project repo history.

# Feishu image multimodal cache (downloaded per-message, cleaned after read).
# Path layout: .cache/images/<feishu_message_id>/<image_key>.<ext>
.cache/images/

